'''圓形大廳與柱廊'''<br />
藝術宮的圓形大廳是一座直徑約{{convert|30|m|ft|lk=on}}高約{{convert|41|m|ft|lk=on}}的圓柱形建築，由八組頎長秀麗的[[科林斯|科林斯]]式圓柱承托著上方雕飾精美的黃色巨大穹頂，每兩組圓柱與穹頂間又組成一個雄偉高大的桃紅色拱形門。每組圓柱皆由四根高約{{convert|12|m|ft|lk=on}}的石柱並列組成，而四根石柱又立於一個高約{{convert|3|m|ft|lk=on}}的花崗石平台上。抬頭看羅馬柱頂端有著許多意大利文藝復興時期風格的雕刻。以圓形大廳為中心，兩旁共延伸出30個科林斯式圓柱組成的柱廊，形成圓弧狀圍繞著前方的人工湖。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |last=Nolte |first=Carl |url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Restored-San-Francisco-Palace-of-Fine-Arts-to-open-2532608.php |title=Restored San Francisco Palace of Fine Arts to open |work=[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]] |date=2011-01-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421064115/http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Restored-San-Francisco-Palace-of-Fine-Arts-to-open-2532608.php |archivedate=2014-04-21 |accessdate=2014-04-21 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news |last=King |first=John |url=http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/New-sense-of-power-at-restored-Palace-of-Fine-Arts-2477915.php |title=New sense of power at restored Palace of Fine Arts |work=[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]] |date=2011-02-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421064836/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/New-sense-of-power-at-restored-Palace-of-Fine-Arts-2477915.php |archivedate=2014-04-21 |accessdate=2014-04-21 }}</ref>
